cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper deals with image manipulation using generative adversarial neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also involves optimization techniques and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) to constrain the output to lie on the natural image manifold. Additionally, the paper deals with graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) as it involves generating novel imagery from user's scribbles.
